Package me.kverna.roger.server.video

Interface VideoFeedListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    VideoDetectionTask, VideoFeedResponseBody
    public interface VideoFeedListener
    Interface for processing video feeds provided by VideoFeedTask.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods

    • Method Detail

      • process

        void process​(net.sf.jipcam.axis.MjpegFrame frame)
        The VideoFeedTask will send chunks of data to this function. Processing can then be done in the implemented object.
        Parameters:
        frame - a frame of video

      • isAlive

        boolean isAlive()
        Should return true when the listener is being used. When this is false, the VideoFeedTask will automatically unsubscribe from this listener.
        Returns:
        true when the listener is being used

      • stop

        void stop()
        Cleanup and finish. Should be called when the attached task stops.
